pop-peers.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/billie-eilish-pop-peers-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/billie-eilish-pop-peers-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/billie-eilish-pop-peers-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/billie-eilish-pop-peers-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/billie-eilish-pop-peers-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish)</a>公开谈论了她的流行音乐同行的成功，并承认他们现在所处的“疯狂”境地。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="543" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/billie-eilish-hit-me-hard-and-soft-review-tracklist-lyrics-3756826"><b>Billie Eilish – “Hit Me Hard and Soft”评论：大胆、精彩、更明亮</b></a></li></ul><p>在最近接受《 <a href="https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/music/story/2024-10-10/billie-eilish-finneas-hit-me-hard-and-soft-grammys-interview" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>洛杉矶时报》</em></a>采访时，这位《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-billie-eilish-levitate-in-new-video-for-birds-of-a-feather-3797975">Birds Of A Feather</a> 》歌手与她的兄弟兼合作者<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Finneas">Finneas</a>一起被问及她是否对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">Chappell Roan</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">Sabrina Carpenter</a>最近的成功感到威胁。</p><p> “你在开玩笑吧？”她回答道。 “我为这些母狗感到高兴。当你达到他们现在所经历的水平时，这是一个疯狂的世界，而且他们做得很好。粉丝们被他们吸引，因为他们太棒了。”</p><p>三人今年的工作都受到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jack-antonoff">杰克·安东诺夫</a>的赞扬，他说<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jack-antonoff-praises-sabrina-carpenter-charli-xcx-and-chappell-roan-for-artist-development-summer-3799943">“小子夏天”应该更名为“艺术家发展夏天”，</a>因为他们各自的粉丝群在多年的材料工作后似乎一夜之间增加了。</p><p>艾利什在谈到突然成名的话题时，回忆起她职业生涯早期的一段时光，当时一名运输安全管理局官员在机场给她拍了一张照片，并说道：“我想，这就是我的生活。 </p><figure id="attachment_3802141" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3802141" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3802141" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/billie-eilish-tour-2024.jpg" alt="比莉·艾利什" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/billie-eilish-tour-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/billie-eilish-tour-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/billie-eilish-tour-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/billie-eilish-tour-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/billie-eilish-tour-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/billie-eilish-tour-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3802141" class="wp-caption-text">比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish) 于 2024 年 9 月 29 日在魁北克省魁北克市 Videotron 中心举行的“HIT ME HARD AND SOFT: THE TOUR”启动仪式上登台表演。图片来源：Kevin Mazur/Getty Images for Live Nation）</figcaption></figure><p> “我再也不敢出门了，我也再也感觉不到自己是一个人了。每个房间都会说，“这是比莉·艾利什！”这最终会让我自杀。”</p><p>罗恩对名誉的类似感受一直成为今年的头条新闻，她最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-says-fame-is-like-an-abusive-ex-husband-3794622">将其与“虐待性的前夫”进行比较</a>，并 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-reveals-severe-depression-diagnosis-3795902">透露自己被诊断出患有“严重抑郁症”</a> ，她将其归因于她的快速崛起。</p><p>此前，她曾在 TikTok 上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-chastises-fans-weird-and-creepy-behaviour-thats-not-normal-3785060">分享了她对“奇怪”和“令人毛骨悚然”的粉丝的看法</a>，指出<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-writes-to-superfans-about-predatory-behaviour-women-dont-owe-you-shit-3786492">所谓“超级粉丝”的“掠夺性行为”</a> ，其中包括“未经同意的身体和社交互动”。</p><p>虽然社交媒体上遭到强烈反对，但几位女性艺术家还是为罗恩辩护，其中包括艾利什和卡彭特，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/katy-perry">凯蒂·佩里</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/muna">穆娜</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/miley-cyrus">麦莉·赛勒斯</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/boygenius">博伊吉尼斯</a>。</p><p>当被问及是否听到罗恩的评论时，艾利什显得很同情，她说：“这里很难，伙计，很难。” </p><figure id="attachment_3794628" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3794628" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3794628" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Dana-Jacobs_WireImage.jpg" alt="查普尔·罗恩.图片来源：Dana Jacobs/WireImage" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Dana-Jacobs_WireImage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Dana-Jacobs_WireImage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Dana-Jacobs_WireImage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Dana-Jacobs_WireImage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Dana-Jacobs_WireImage-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Dana-Jacobs_WireImage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3794628" class="wp-caption-text">查普尔·罗恩.图片来源：Dana Jacobs/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p>这位歌手还表示， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-responds-to-variety-outing-her-i-like-boys-and-girls-leave-me-alone-about-it-please-3552827">在<em>《综艺》</em>去年在一次采访中似乎揭露了她的身份</a>后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-says-she-never-wants-to-talk-about-her-sexuality-ever-ever-ever-again-3800971">她再也不想“永远、永远、永远”谈论自己的性取向</a>，这成为了一个大新闻。 “我还低估了我说的话会被吹成全世界最大的新闻。”她说。 “这太不自然了。”</p><p>卡彭特透露，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>曾<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-reveals-taylor-swifts-advice-on-handling-fame-3800028">与她分享了如何处理名誉和压力的建议</a>，她说：“你会发现周围的人让你感到安全，并从那里出发。”</p><p>与此同时，今年早些时候与 Eilish 联手制作《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-billie-eilish-guess-remix-the-dare-finneas-3780251">Guess</a> 》的 XCX 周四（10 月 10 日） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-brat-remix-album-listening-party-new-york-stream-photos-footage-3801703">在纽约举办了一场亲密的聆听派对，庆祝新混音专辑《Brat And it&#39;s Completely Different But Also Still Brat》</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-on-the-success-of-chappell-roan-charli-xcx-and-sabrina-carpenter-its-a-crazy-world-when-you-get-to-the-level-theyre-experiencing-right-now-3802133">Billie Eilish 的帖子谈论 Chappell Roan、Charli XCX 和 Sabrina Carpenter 的成功：“当你达到他们现在所经历的水平时，这是一个疯狂的世界”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
