情翻唱 Radiohead 的《Fake Plastic Trees》</a>后，首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Finneas-and-Radioheads-Thom-Yorke.-CREDIT_-Emma-McIntyre_Getty-Images-for-W-Magazine-and-Daniele-Venturelli_WireImage.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Finneas-and-Radioheads-Thom-Yorke.-CREDIT_-Emma-McIntyre_Getty-Images-for-W-Magazine-and-Daniele-Venturelli_WireImage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Finneas-and-Radioheads-Thom-Yorke.-CREDIT_-Emma-McIntyre_Getty-Images-for-W-Magazine-and-Daniele-Venturelli_WireImage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Finneas-and-Radioheads-Thom-Yorke.-CREDIT_-Emma-McIntyre_Getty-Images-for-W-Magazine-and-Daniele-Venturelli_WireImage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Finneas-and-Radioheads-Thom-Yorke.-CREDIT_-Emma-McIntyre_Getty-Images-for-W-Magazine-and-Daniele-Venturelli_WireImage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Finneas-and-Radioheads-Thom-Yorke.-CREDIT_-Emma-McIntyre_Getty-Images-for-W-Magazine-and-Daniele-Venturelli_WireImage-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Finneas-and-Radioheads-Thom-Yorke.-CREDIT_-Emma-McIntyre_Getty-Images-for-W-Magazine-and-Daniele-Venturelli_WireImage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/finneas">Finneas</a>在 BBC Radio 1 的 Live Lounge 中报道了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/radiohead">Radiohead</a>的“Fake Plastic Trees”。看看下面。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/finneas-cover-interview-2021-debut-solo-album-optimist-billie-eilish-3059733"><b>封面上 – Finneas：“我不知道还有什么比我和 Billie 的创意联系更牢固的了”</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>去年，Radiohead 主唱 Thom Yorke <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/thom-yorke-why-he-cried-hearing-fake-plastic-trees-played-back-to-him-3496671">透露，当他第一次听到《Fake Plastic Trees》播放给他听时，他哭了</a>，并表示在 1995 年录制歌曲时，看到<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jeff-buckley">Jeff Buckley 的</a>现场表演帮助他拥抱并适应了自己在歌曲中的声音。</p><p>从那时起，许多音乐家分享了他们对这首歌的看法。 2012 年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/frank-ocean">Frank Ocean</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/what-do-you-think-of-frank-oceans-radiohead-cover-4849">在纽约的 Spotify 活动中</a>翻唱了这首歌， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kelly-clarkson">Kelly Clarkson</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kelly-clarkson-shares-studio-version-of-radioheads-fake-plastic-trees-3243676">在 2022 年分享了这首歌的完整录音室版本</a>，2020 年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/phoebe-bridgers">Phoebe Bridgers</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arlo-parks">Arlo Parks</a>联手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-phoebe-bridgers-arlo-parks-cover-radiohead-fake-plastic-trees-2746527">演奏了钢琴版本</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paramore">Paramore</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hayley-williams">Hayley Williams</a>也<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-hayley-williams-tender-cover-of-radioheads-fake-plastic-trees-2723874">以“对有史以来最好的乐队之一的钦佩”的方式翻唱了这首歌曲</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/holly-humberstone">Holly Humberstone</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/holly-humberstone-covers-radiohead-fake-plastic-trees-radar-2718306">在 2020 年发布了她自己的原声版本</a>。</p><p>现在，芬尼斯在新的 Live Lounge 表演中分享了他对这首影响深远的热门歌曲的看法。芬尼斯独自一人用钢琴演奏这首 1995 年的歌曲，给人一种令人难忘、深情的感觉。看看下面。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="FINNEAS - 现场休息室中的假塑料树（Radiohead 封面）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/KWV-H-d-0uo?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>约克<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/thom-yorke-says-hes-fan-billie-eilish-nobodys-telling-2525334">赞扬了芬尼斯的妹妹</a>兼创意合作伙伴<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">比莉·艾利什（Billie Eilish）</a> ，他透露自己是这位歌手的粉丝：“她正在做自己的事情。没有人告诉她该怎么做，”他说。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilishs-manager-reveals-what-thom-yorke-said-when-he-met-her-2533968">芬尼斯后来将这句话描述为“任何人对你说过的最酷的话”。</a></p><p> Finneas 是最新在标志性 Live Lounge 表演的乐队。上周， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-fontaines-d-c-s-woozy-cover-of-lana-del-reys-say-yes-to-heaven-3799007">Fontaines DC 翻唱了 Lana Del Rey 的《Say Yes To Heaven》</a> ，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-dua-lipa-cover-cleo-sols-sunshine-in-radio-1-live-lounge-3754309">Dua Lipa 在五月份翻唱了 Cleo Sol 的《Sunshine》</a> 。</p><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/check-out-sabrina-carpenters-stripped-back-cover-of-chappell-roans-good-luck-babe-for-bbc-radio-one-live-lounge-3766709">萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter) 分享了她版本的查普尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan) 的歌曲《祝你好运，宝贝！》(Good Luck, Babe!)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-last-dinner-party-cover-troye-sivans-one-of-your-girls-in-the-radio-1-live-lounge-nme-radar-3583280">The Last Evening Party 在 Live Lounge 首秀中翻唱了 Troye Sivan 的《One Of Your Girls》</a> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3798240" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3798240" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3798240" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024_finneas_getty_2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024_finneas_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024_finneas_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024_finneas_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024_finneas_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024_finneas_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024_finneas_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3798240" class="wp-caption-text">芬尼斯在 LA28 奥运会交接庆典上表演 图片来源：Emma McIntyre/Getty Images for LA28</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/finneas-announces-for-cryin-out-loud-2025-north-american-tour-buy-tickets-3800278">在其他新闻中，芬尼斯最近宣布了一次巡演</a>，以庆祝他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/finneas-announces-second-album-for-cryin-out-loud-with-hopeful-title-track-3782171">新发行的第二张专辑“For Cryin&#39; Out Loud”</a> 。您可以<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/finneas-announces-for-cryin-out-loud-2025-north-american-tour-buy-tickets-3800278">在此处</a>找到完整的日期列表，并<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Ffinneas-tickets%2Fartist%2F2550584" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处</a>查看美国和欧洲的门票、 <a href="https://ticketmaster-au.tm7566.net/c/2862475/431533/7566?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com.au%2Ffinneas-tickets%2Fartist%2F2550584" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处查看澳大利亚的日期</a>以及<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Ffinneas-tickets%2Fartist%2F5279208" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处查看英国的门票</a>。</p><p>在此之前，他为妹妹<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a>的第三张录音室专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/billie-eilish-hit-me-hard-and-soft-review-tracklist-lyrics-3756826">《Hit Me Hard And Soft》做出了贡献，</a>并凭借《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-announces-what-was-i-made-for-for-barbie-soundtrack-3465802">What Was I Made For</a> 》第二次获得奥斯卡奖，该专辑是他为<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/barbie-review-margot-robbie-ryan-gosling-3470019">芭比娃娃</a></em>配乐共同创作和制作的。</p><p>这位制作人兼音乐家也首次亮相电视配乐，为即将推出的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/apple-tv">Apple TV+</a>限定剧集<em>《免责声明》</em>进行创作。</p><p>在对<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/billie-eilish-hit-me-hard-and-soft-review-tracklist-lyrics-3756826">Billie Eilish LP 的四星评论</a>中， <em>NME</em>分享道：“《Hit Me Hard And Soft》仍然是独一无二的，它描绘了一位进入青年期的非凡天才，探索她的酷儿特质，体验情感上的刺激和（有时）灾难。”追逐激情或坠入爱河。在尝试为自己写一张专辑时，她制作了一张比她以前做过的任何专辑都更能引起共鸣的专辑。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-finneas-soulful-cover-of-radioheads-fake-plastic-trees-3802122">Watch Finneas 深情翻唱 Radiohead 的《Fake Plastic Trees》</a>后，首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
